title: Un zoo pas comme les autres
overview: Un zoo pas comme les autres stars Emilie and Clifford and their "babies": more than 150 animals that have taken refuge at their home, Miller Zoo. Kangaroos, tigers, lions, lynx, tamanduas, black bears, wolves, coyotes, raccoons, moose, etc. Some stay there for life, while others are rehabilitated to be released into the wild.
